I"1<p>Getting Jekyll installed and ready-to-go should only take a few minutes. If it ever becomes a pain in the ass, please <a href="https://github.com/jekyll/jekyll/issues/new">file an issue</a> (or submit a pull request) describing the issue you encountered and how we might make the process easier.</p>

<h3 id="requirements">Requirements</h3>

<p>Installing Jekyll is easy and straight-forward, but there are a few requirements you’ll need to make sure your system has before you start.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/downloads/">Ruby</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://rubygems.org/pages/download">RubyGems</a></li>
  <li>Linux, Unix, or Mac OS X</li>
  <li><a href="http://nodejs.org/">NodeJS</a>, or another JavaScript runtime (for CoffeeScript support).</li>
</ul>

<!-- more -->

